N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 145-2.0 - Purpose

State Regulations

The purpose of this Subpart is to set forth the methods and
procedures governing the availability, location and nature of those records of
the Division of the Budget subject to the provisions of article 6-A of the

Public Officers Law, known as the Personal Privacy Protection Law, and the
rules of the Committee on Open Government. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9
§§
145-2.0

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
